{
  "texts": [
    "Part-of-speech is a class of words with grammatical properties that play a role in the syntax of similar sentences [237].",
    "POS-Tagging has similarities to NER, which tag the corpus.",
    "Labels on POS Tags use nouns, verbs, adjectives, adverbs, exclamations, and others [239].",
    "Labels on NER are defined based on entities such as a person (PER), location (LOC), organization (ORG), and others.",
    "POS tags can be implemented in any domain because the POS structure has the same pattern in all disciplines."
  ]
}